reviewText: I really enjoyed this when I saw it when it came out so I got it to give to a grandson so he could see if he liked it or not.
Starts out a little slow but very good movie
Certainly grade 'B' but very original S-F and Joe Morton does a great job as the lead character. Dated, however.
Good story. I was hoping for a better quality video transfer. Video Image is blurry and about equal to low quality VHS.
